    : stats.review > 0
      ? `${stats.review} ׳׳׳׳¨׳™׳ ׳׳—׳›׳™׳ ׳׳‘׳“׳™׳§׳”.`
      : "׳׳™׳ ׳¦׳•׳•׳׳¨ ׳‘׳§׳‘׳•׳§ ׳›׳¨׳’׳¢. ׳׳₪׳©׳¨ ׳׳¢׳‘׳•׳¨ ׳׳™׳¦׳™׳¨׳” ׳׳• ׳׳©׳™׳₪׳•׳¨ ׳”׳©׳™׳¨׳•׳×׳™׳.";
